<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7380974>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Acantholichen dendroideus. A. Habit of the species growing on mosses. B–C. Thallus showing ascendant, densely and dichotomously branched microsquamules; scale in B = 1 cm, scale in C = 0.5 mm. D–E. Close up showing microfruticose, coral-like squamules; scale in D = 0.1 mm, scale in E = 0.2 mm. Photos by V. Marcano." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7380974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7380972>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution of Dictyonema s.lat. species in Venezuela. 1. Acantholichen dendroideus. 2. Cyphellostereum mucuyense. 3. Dictyonema andinum. 4. D. duidense. 5. D. laurae. 6. D. subinvolutum. 7. D. subsericeum. 8. D. umbricola. A. Andes. B. Cerro Duida." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7380972/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

